    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a dependable ride that's full of character? This vehicle is a solid choice for anyone needing a functional and reliable daily driver! While it shows some honest signs of use from its time on the road, it has been well-maintained and is ready to serve its next owner faithfully. It\u2019s a practical, road-ready companion that still has plenty of miles to go!",
