    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound and have been serviced regularly, ensuring it starts and runs smoothly. However, please note that the car shows signs of its age and mileage; the exterior has some minor scratches and paint chips, and the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. It is a solid, functional vehicle that has many miles left in it, perfect for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. All major systems like the AC and brakes are in working order.",
