    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting. While it is mechanically sound and starts without issue, it does show its age with some cosmetic imperfections including minor door dings, paint fading on the hood, and some wear on the interior upholstery. There is a small oil leak that doesn't affect performance but will need monitoring, and the tires have about 40% tread remaining. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
