    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with a factory limited-slip differential and recently refreshed bushings. Meticulously maintained, the double VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014critical for long-term structural integrity. While showing minor signs of driver-focused use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are exceptional. This is a driver\u2019s specification, balancing raw performance with the refined ergonomics of a modern classic.",
